code: protected Post processInsert(Exchange exchange) {     LOG.debug("Trying to create a new blog post with {}", exchange.getIn().getBody()).     return servicePosts.create(exchange.getIn().getBody(Post.class)). }

protected Post processUpdate(Exchange exchange) {     LOG.debug("Trying to update the post {} with id {}", exchange.getIn().getBody(), this.getConfiguration().getId()).     return servicePosts.update(this.getConfiguration().getId(), exchange.getIn().getBody(Post.class)). }

protected Post processDelete(Exchange exchange) {     LOG.debug("Trying to delete a post with id {}", this.getConfiguration().getId()).     if (this.getConfiguration().isForce()) {         return servicePosts.forceDelete(this.getConfiguration().getId()).getPrevious().     } else {         return servicePosts.delete(this.getConfiguration().getId()).     } }
